# Header
# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# *type* field is required, you can pick one in belows:
#   - feat: new feature
#   - fix: fix bugs
#   - docs: documentation
#   - style: just only format code, does not affect results
#   - refactor: reconstruction
#   - test: add test case
#   - chore: changes of building process or tools
#   - revert: undo previous commits
# *scope* field is optional, you can write something what be affected
# *subject* field is required, you can write the short description of commit

# Body
# <description>
# *description* is required, a detailed description

# Footer
# <incompatiblie actions> or <close issues>
